---
// RA has no Font Awesome brand glyph and no public simple/monochrome SVG
// mark the way Beatport does — following EpkIcon.astro's precedent (a
// custom-drawn mark for platforms without one) rather than tracing a
// vector approximation of their real logo, this is a plain text lettermark
// sized and weighted to sit at the same visual weight as the other custom
// icons in this row.
---

<svg class="ra-svg" viewBox="0 0 44 28" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <text x="22" y="21" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="24" font-weight="700" letter-spacing="1" fill="white" text-anchor="middle">RA</text>
</svg>

<style>
  .ra-svg {
    height: 22px;
    width: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ra-svg {
      height: 18px;
    }
  }
</style>
